  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/bfbccca4cb037a34fe3f65438d737841.avif?t=1774181354\" width=600 height=160 /></span>Eat onigiri and bond with everyone! The ultimate onigiri action game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A platformer where you control a character whose abilities change by eating onigiri, exploring and solving the secrets of a strange island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/aec22726fa7fd1b7473ef9840ca200da.poster.avif?t=1774181354\" width=600 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/aec22726fa7fd1b7473ef9840ca200da.webm?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/aec22726fa7fd1b7473ef9840ca200da.mp4?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mysterious island that I drifted and arrived at.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This enigmatic island had a level design feeling in its terrain and the arrangement of onigiri ...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/b06e26baad4d77ca041a98dfdd2504fd.poster.avif?t=1774181354\" width=600 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/b06e26baad4d77ca041a98dfdd2504fd.webm?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/b06e26baad4d77ca041a98dfdd2504fd.mp4?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My state changes when I eat an onigiri.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As my state changes, so do the controls and my interactions with objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the situation changes, the dynamics with onigiri and 'everyone' also change.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each stage offers a bit of a challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8x8 pixel characters in a 160x90 pixel world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/e99fbbf96ed901f361133093aa6f36ac.poster.avif?t=1774181354\" width=600 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/e99fbbf96ed901f361133093aa6f36ac.webm?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/e99fbbf96ed901f361133093aa6f36ac.mp4?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using the directional pad and two buttons, you can jump, shoot, and eat bitten onigiri. That's all you need. Memorize the body movements for different situations, overcome obstacles, and clear the stages to unravel the mysteries of the island!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/517969a730ea0871ccc7b896f5afbac0.webp?t=1774181354\" width=600 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>\"</strong></i>Isn't it cool that I can double jump by eating an onigiri in mid-air?!<i><strong>\"</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Streaming Guidelines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game allows video streaming and monetization with no restrictions for both individuals and businesses.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/bfbccca4cb037a34fe3f65438d737841.avif?t=1774181354\" width=600 height=160 /></span>Eat onigiri and bond with everyone! The ultimate onigiri action game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A platformer where you control a character whose abilities change by eating onigiri, exploring and solving the secrets of a strange island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/aec22726fa7fd1b7473ef9840ca200da.poster.avif?t=1774181354\" width=600 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/aec22726fa7fd1b7473ef9840ca200da.webm?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/aec22726fa7fd1b7473ef9840ca200da.mp4?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mysterious island that I drifted and arrived at.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This enigmatic island had a level design feeling in its terrain and the arrangement of onigiri ...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/b06e26baad4d77ca041a98dfdd2504fd.poster.avif?t=1774181354\" width=600 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/b06e26baad4d77ca041a98dfdd2504fd.webm?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/b06e26baad4d77ca041a98dfdd2504fd.mp4?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My state changes when I eat an onigiri.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As my state changes, so do the controls and my interactions with objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the situation changes, the dynamics with onigiri and 'everyone' also change.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each stage offers a bit of a challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8x8 pixel characters in a 160x90 pixel world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/e99fbbf96ed901f361133093aa6f36ac.poster.avif?t=1774181354\" width=600 height=58 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/e99fbbf96ed901f361133093aa6f36ac.webm?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/e99fbbf96ed901f361133093aa6f36ac.mp4?t=1774181354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using the directional pad and two buttons, you can jump, shoot, and eat bitten onigiri. That's all you need. Memorize the body movements for different situations, overcome obstacles, and clear the stages to unravel the mysteries of the island!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703970/extras/517969a730ea0871ccc7b896f5afbac0.webp?t=1774181354\" width=600 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>\"</strong></i>Isn't it cool that I can double jump by eating an onigiri in mid-air?!<i><strong>\"</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Streaming Guidelines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game allows video streaming and monetization with no restrictions for both individuals and businesses.</p>",
